Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.29,0:01:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,000)}第6话 小樱与母亲的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.09,0:01:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天因为时间很晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.02,0:01:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想走近路 从学校后的森林回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.81,0:01:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.64,0:02:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.04,0:02:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪子，你说的是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是你看错了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.91,0:02:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.41,0:02:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说这件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最怕鬼故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，为了证实这件事的真假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去调查一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天社团会提早结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们找利佳大家一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.47,0:02:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个森林里面不是有个悬壁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.54,0:02:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要走到那里就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要是有鬼怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们快逃就没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之不会有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.49,0:03:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息时间结束了，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都喜欢鬼故事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会发生很可怕的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还要去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，你陪我去好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.44,0:03:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是别去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别怕，现在天还很亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，是啊，你别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，我妈妈的生日快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们觉得我送什么礼物好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.13,0:03:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千春，你妈妈喜欢做甜点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以送可爱的甜点盘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.70,0:03:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甜点盘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.80,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，你觉得呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，别在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.67,0:04:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔，下周日就是妈妈的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是乌鸦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能要等到晚上才会出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个长发的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有尖尖的耳朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个眼睛转来转去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.68,0:05:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张着粉红色大嘴露出牙齿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.49,0:05:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大肉包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.79,0:05:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说我看到了大肉包耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很可怕耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来小樱你怕幽灵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.54,0:05:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却不怕跟库洛牌战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.41,0:05:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是怕莫名其妙的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.51,0:05:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少我知道库洛牌是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.98,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的理论让人似懂非懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.36,0:06:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是每个人看到的都不一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这种牌吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备吃晚餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.80,0:06:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望小可早点恢复原形 当我的保镳就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.27,0:06:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若想让我恢复 最少还要收回"火牌"跟"地牌"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.58,0:06:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的原形可是很帅的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很帅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.05,0:06:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，你喜欢吃面对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.26,0:06:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢这张照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是妈妈16岁时拍的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈叫抚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.37,0:06:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中学就开始当模特儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些登在杂志的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.38,0:06:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有爸爸拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.28,0:06:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全都收藏着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.56,0:07:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，她是世上最美丽、最温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最完美的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈过世时我才3岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不太记得她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.64,0:07:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过爸爸常常提起妈妈的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜欢妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，不快点吃会凉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.98,0:07:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也要快点 不然会赶搭不上新干线的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸跟哥哥都出去了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥去打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.83,0:07:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是出差开研讨会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸准备了布丁喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.23,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把哥哥的份也吃了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶!布丁!布丁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，这里是木之本家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.68,0:08:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们又去森林了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，千春打电话给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.22,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次跟其他同学一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果又出现了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是幽灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.07,0:08:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛魔法使吓成这样像什么话嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是有人受伤吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.85,0:08:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，千春她们五个人一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来看到幽灵太惊讶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人跌倒伤得不轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是库洛牌就一定要抓到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.66,0:08:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是捍卫左邻右舍和平的库洛魔法使嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是幽灵怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.47,0:09:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之不去看看便无法查出真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，“飞”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是妈妈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.77,0:10:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.48,0:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.33,0:10:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边是悬壁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱!小樱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.02,0:10:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.59,0:11:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.09,0:11:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件衣服是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.33,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱的衣服正在洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我奶奶帮你换的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.74,0:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔，雪兔哥跟爷爷奶奶住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥跟我说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.65,0:11:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，你从悬壁上掉下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.42,0:12:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你记得吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.65,0:12:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过吓了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.06,0:12:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走在路上 看到你从空中掉下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.73,0:12:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那雪兔哥你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴太阳眼镜的姊姊们来接她走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很担心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说我会联络桃矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就说请我照顾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟他说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别担心，他不会骂你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，小可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.72,0:12:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只橘色的玩偶是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.29,0:12:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世说她今天先帮你保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，你再休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.48,0:13:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在悬壁上看见我妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.15,0:13:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我妈妈的幽灵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.86,0:13:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我哥哥说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.83,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵出现都是有理由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.30,0:13:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈为什么在那里出现呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，如果真的是你妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.04,0:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会让你遭遇危险吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.44,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪，不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.53,0:13:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.50,0:13:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱说她见到妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小学后面的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桃矢，你见过去世的妈妈吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过不是在学校后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙会这么怕幽灵跟妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因为我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很小的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.55,0:14:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就骗她有透明女鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有白发老爷爷飘起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.02,0:14:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以小樱才会这么害怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.66,0:14:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她虽然没看见还是会幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是呜呜地哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.73,0:14:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是常看到你妈吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我上中学以后就看不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可能是没有妈妈太孤单了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是她只是想见妈妈一面罢了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱也有一些心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天别骂她喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.29,0:14:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你那么疼爱小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.46,0:14:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那平常就别欺负她了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有我能欺负她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有听说过"恋妹情结"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.21,0:15:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天请假耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，完全没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.45,0:15:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥叫我休息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我没帮上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.73,0:15:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那道光到底是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.24,0:15:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈在那座森林里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.51,0:15:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是每个人看到的都不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有小樱你一个人看到的是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.51,0:15:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次还是放弃比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.78,0:15:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管它是库洛牌还是幽灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.25,0:16:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都拥有足以弹开我 并让我昏倒的魔力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是我要求你找回纸牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.39,0:16:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不想看到小樱你受伤或是哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可，你太帅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.34,0:16:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.17,0:16:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还想去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.71,0:16:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是纸牌，就必须想办法收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.39,0:16:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥以前说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈已经不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我长大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.63,0:16:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很放心去了天上很漂亮的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么妈妈为什么会在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.58,0:16:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想问她到底想对我说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.82,0:17:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，你要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再从悬壁上掉下去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,务必要特别小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.26,0:17:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是还会再出现吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.43,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会，我的直觉准没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.58,0:17:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.19,0:17:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟照片一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.99,0:17:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么这次大家都看见同样东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是妈妈吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.97,0:18:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，你很孤单吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟我在一起是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.68,0:18:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别走!妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.45,0:18:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能去那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你别走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.24,0:18:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.18,0:18:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是你妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会让你遭遇危险吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.10,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.93,0:18:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈不会这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她绝不会这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.04,0:19:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“飞”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.05,0:19:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.02,0:19:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是库洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢复你原来的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.04,0:19:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.12,0:19:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是"幻牌(illusion)"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.76,0:19:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪每个人看到的都不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.76,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"幻牌"能让人看到自己想看到的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.50,0:20:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它反应出每个人心中的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然大家都不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.11,0:20:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，第一次来时我肚子好饿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直想吃肉包子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家所看到的幽灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是自己觉得最可怕的东西 所以才会看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我们会看到小樱的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.02,0:20:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是因为看过照片\N又认为这次一定会出现才看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.03,0:20:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么会被弹开?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.36,0:20:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为小樱看到妈妈兴奋的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在太强烈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈不是孤单的待在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能见到她当然很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.64,0:20:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过她待在漂亮的天堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会更高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，你这么努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈一定会放心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.09,0:21:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这次可能让她担心了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.10,0:21:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!要迟到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期天也要穿制服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.31,0:21:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要参加社团啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.09,0:21:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈，祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.62,0:21:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好爱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我出门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.31,0:21:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次我的确有点担心 所以回来看看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.34,0:21:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.07,0:23:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}包在小可身上!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.11,0:23:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.14,0:23:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家有没有帮忙做家事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.44,0:23:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有?那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.55,0:23:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又到了每周必看的"包在小可身上"时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.12,0:23:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.39,0:23:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦!又是战服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.82,0:23:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上周没为大家介绍，应该很想念吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.09,0:23:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次与以往的设计有点不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.03,0:23:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有种未来时代感觉，很新鲜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.30,0:24:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世的品味又迈向新境界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.77,0:24:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别是独特的肩膀设计很棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.11,0:24:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又到了"小可观察时间"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.78,0:24:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个通讯机真的很好用喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.15,0:24:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻便结实，感应度好，紧急时特别方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.92,0:24:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是高科技产品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.62,0:24:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?知世每集都花费心思在设计吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.66,0:24:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我也不能马马虎虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.79,0:24:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让这个单元更加精采
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.76,0:24:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.20,0:24:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将前往美术馆写生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.57,0:24:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我让小可当模特儿练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.07,0:24:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥却说我太吵会被赶出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.48,0:24:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.31,0:24:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.61,0:24:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?我们怎么会在外面呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.59,0:24:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛魔法使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.05,0:24:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“小樱首次挑战当怪盗”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.72,0:24:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也与小樱一起解除封印!
